In addition to the use of topic modelling, further research could focus on taking our project to a worldwide level. 
Some interesting results could be found by comparing several countries with greater cultural and political differences. 
The state level within the US was too small to find any clear variations, but a comparison between countries with a different developmental level sure is an interesting area of research. 

Further research could also focus on a longer or a shorter time period. 
It could be interesting to see if the sentiment varies over months, or in a very short time period such as a day, or an hour. 

